original_title: WWE: Legends of Wrestling - Hulk Hogan and Bob Backlund
overview: In one of the most popular shows on WWE's on demand channel, panels that include WWE Hall of Famers Jim Ross and Dusty Rhodes discuss the life and times of the legendary Hulk Hogan and Bob Backlund.
title: WWE: Legends of Wrestling - Hulk Hogan and Bob Backlund
